        <abstract>
            <p>Convinced length of stamens has no relation to powers of fertilisation in many plants.</p> 
<p>Suggests experiments on <hi rend="italic">Pelargonium</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Phlox</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Advises about use of microscope.</p>
